        "body": "<p>It turned out that the problem was caused by the <strong>latest versions of Surefire and Failsaf<\/strong>e. The version 3.5.3 breaks the detection of failed scenarios somehow. Everything runs fine with version 3.5.2.<br />\nI do not know who to blame for this but let's see what the future brings.<\/p>\n",
